               <p>NATHANIEL GODFREY. I <rs id="t18160403-172-viclabel856" type="occupation">sell soap</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160403-172-victim1196 t18160403-172-viclabel856"></join>; I lost three pounds on the 23rd of March in the morning; I did not see it taken.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18160403-172-person1197">
                  THOMAS 
                  WEATHERHEAD
               <interp inst="t18160403-172-person1197" type="surname" value="WEATHERHEAD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160403-172-person1197" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160403-172-person1197" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . From my up-stairs window, I saw the prisoner and another lad lurking about the prosecutor's shop. The prisoner went in and moved a cake of soap about a yard; his companion then tapped at the window, and he came out. They then both crossed over to my side of the way. I then went down stairs to watch them more narrowly, and the prisoner then went in again and brought the soap out.</p>
